module expands the view of literacy to include reading, writing, and other
forms of media. The concepts in this module will help adult educators reflect
on current approaches and consider new strategies to ultimately help adult
learners see why reading and writing truly matter, therefore providing them
with the motivation to persevere even when presented with difficulties.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{4fb87be1-2965-455b-b36d-82060d6d7a36}{217}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:10,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;a data-copystatus="32" data-copyfailedreason="0" data-clipservice-ccpid="8879b93b-add1-427a-94e1-130421444fa3" data-clipservice-version="0" data-clipservice-location="Y31rebrB5kOrm55r1FkqRV9odHRwOi8vYnkzcGVwZjAwMDFlODUxL3BvZHMvcG9kQ2xpcC5zdmM_UG9kU0lEPV8uXy5fLjg1ZTFmMWFiLWNhMjctMTZhMy0xMDQxLWVlOTk1YThkOWM2OS0uLS4tLg2" data-clipservice-dc="US1" data-clipservice-type="slide" data-clipservice-count="1" data-clipservice-cut="false" data-clipservice-isemptyplaceholder="false" data-pkey="753703b1-7b9f-4274-99cc-2c4c0aa42a11" data-timestamp="Fri, 17 Feb 2023 21:46:29 GMT" data-clipboardasbytes-url="https://usc-powerpoint.officeapps.live.com/pods/GetClipboardBytes.ashx?Id=8879b93b-add1-427a-94e1-130421444fa3&amp;amp;DC=US1&amp;amp;pkey=753703b1-7b9f-4274-99cc-2c4c0aa42a11&amp;amp;wdwaccluster=US1&amp;amp;DataType=slide" data-sessionid="a43d07fa-56e4-bf66-0de7-72c8263c08aa" data-shapeids="" data-slideid="900560487+388" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;a data-copystatus="32" data-copyfailedreason="0" data-clipservice-ccpid="8879b93b-add1-427a-94e1-130421444fa3" data-clipservice-version="0" data-clipservice-location="Y31reb